<p><b>Marcel Mauss</b> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1872-05-10"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="05-10"><a href="/wiki/May_10" title="May 10">May 10</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1872" title="1872">1872</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1950-02-10"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="02-10"><a href="/wiki/February_10" title="February 10">February 10</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1950" title="1950">1950</a></span>) was a <a href="/wiki/France" title="France">French</a> <a href="/wiki/Sociologist" title="Sociologist" class="mw-redirect">sociologist</a>.</p>
